    "image_with_text_g4DheV": {
      "type": "text-with-image",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "subheading": "Who is a Carbon38",
        "title": "Ambassador",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/workout_1-1200x1200_1000x_7f254f9d-a36c-4cbc-bb61-b63af7a785fb.webp",
        "image_position": "right",
        "content": "<p>The Carbon38 Ambassador is a leader in the fitness industry and the best in their field. They are magnetic and authentic influencers. They keep their clients and communities motivated in innovative and exciting ways.</p><p>Check out <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/teamc38/\"><em><strong>@TeamC38</strong></em></a> on Instagram to see our community in action.</p>",
        "link_text": "",
        "link_url": ""
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_Q684Rj": {
      "type": "text-with-image",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "subheading": "The Carbon38 Ambassador program",
        "title": "How We're Different",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/community_1000x_a0715f87-f7bf-42ea-896d-7f559e629bf6.webp",
        "image_position": "left",
        "content": "<p>Simply put, community.</p><p></p><p>Katie Warner Johnson, our CEO, was the original Carbon38 Ambassador. Her experience as a celebrity fitness instructor left her determined to create a new kind of ambassador program—one that was thoughtful, engaged, and committed to the growth of its members. By fostering connectivity and supporting each Ambassador in their journey, we've been able to build a network of <strong>over 7,000 Ambassadors</strong> <strong>worldwide.</strong></p>",
        "link_text": "",
        "link_url": ""
      }
    },
